Example Program Run:

% ./database_bash.db DB new "Example"
New database created
% ./database_bash.db DB add Ford Mustang 2008 "blue with white stripes"
Successfully added a record to the database
% ./database_bash.db DB add Mitsubishi Lancer 2009 white
Successfully added a record to the database
% ./database_bash.db DB add Toyota "Camry LE" 2004 black
Successfully added a record to the database
% ./database_bash.db DB add Porsche "Cayenne S" 2007 red
Successfully added a record to the database
% ./database_bash.db DB show all
Example
Ford, Mustang, 2008, blue with white stripes
Mitsubishi, Lancer, 2009, white
Toyota, Camry LE, 2004, black
Porsche, Cayenne S, 2007, red
% ./database_bash.db DB delete single 2
1 record deleted
% ./database_bash.db DB show all
Example
Ford, Mustang, 2008, blue with white stripes
Toyota, Camry LE, 2004, black
Porsche, Cayenne S, 2007, red
% cat DB
